 <!DOCTYPE html>
 <html lang="zh-TW">
 <head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>DownloadYT — YouTube 影片下載器</title>
   <script>window.BASE_PATH = '<%= basePath %>';</script>
   <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= basePath %>/styles.css">
   <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
   <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   <style>
     .section-enter { animation: fadeSlideIn 0.4s ease-out; }
     @keyframes fadeSlideIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
     @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.6; } }
     .progress-complete .progress-fill { animation: pulse 0.8s ease-in-out 3; }
     .format-option { transition: transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
     .format-option:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }
     .format-option.selected { transform: scale(1.02); }
     .spinner { animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite, fadeSlideIn 0.3s ease-out; }
     @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
     .modal-overlay {
       position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
       background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); z-index: 1000; display: flex;
       align-items: center; justify-content: center;
       animation: fadeSlideIn 0.25s ease-out;
     }
     .modal-overlay.hidden { display: none; }
     .modal-box {
       background: #1a1a2e; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 12px;
       max-width: 760px; width: 90%; max-height: 85vh; overflow-y: auto;
       padding: 32px; color: #eee; position: relative;
     }
     .modal-box h2 { color: #e94560; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.3rem; }
     .modal-box h3 { color: #ccc; margin: 24px 0 10px; font-size: 1rem; }
     .modal-box code { background: #111; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #4caf50; }
     .modal-box pre { background: #111; padding: 14px; border-radius: 8px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #ccc; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; }
     .modal-close { position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 20px; background: none; border: none; color: #888; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; }
     .modal-close:hover { color: #e94560; }
     .help-btn { background: none; border: 1px solid #555; color: #888; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: all .2s; }
    .help-btn:hover { border-color: #e94560; color: #e94560; }
     .instruction-section {
       text-align: center;
       margin: 16px auto 24px;
       max-width: 100%;
     }
     .instruction-image {
       max-width: 100%;
       height: auto;
       border-radius: 10px;
       box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
     }
  </style>
 </head>
 <body>
   <div class="container">
     <header>
       <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
         <div>
           <h1>YouTube 影片下載器</h1>
           <p class="subtitle">高清 MP4 影片與 M4A 音訊下載</p>
         </div>
         <button id="helpBtn" class="help-btn">說明</button>
       </div>
     </header>
 
     <main>
       <div class="search-box">
         <input type="text" id="videoUrl" placeholder="貼上 YouTube 影片連結，按 Enter 自動分析..." autofocus />
        </div>
  
        <!-- 使用說明圖片 -->
        <div class="instruction-section">
           <img src="<%= basePath %>/說明.png" alt="使用說明" class="instruction-image" />
         </div>
 
        <div id="loading" class="hidden">
         <div class="spinner"></div>
         <p>正在分析...</p>
       </div>
 
       <div id="videoInfo" class="hidden">
         <div class="video-preview">
           <div class="thumbnail-container">
             <img id="videoThumbnail" src="" alt="影片縮圖" />
           </div>
           <div class="video-details">
             <h2 id="videoTitle"></h2>
             <p id="videoMeta"></p>
           </div>
         </div>
         <div class="format-section">
           <h3>選擇下載格式</h3>
           <div class="format-tabs">
             <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="video">影片 (MP4)</button>
             <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="audio">音訊 (M4A)</button>
           </div>
           <div id="videoFormats" class="format-list active">
             <div class="format-group">
               <h4>高清畫質</h4>
               <div class="format-options" id="hdFormats"></div>
             </div>
             <div class="format-group">
               <h4>普通畫質</h4>
               <div class="format-options" id="sdFormats"></div>
             </div>
           </div>
           <div id="audioFormats" class="format-list">
             <div class="format-options" id="mp3Options"></div>
           </div>
           <button id="downloadBtn" class="download-btn" disabled>開始下載</button>
         </div>
       </div>
 
       <div id="downloadSection" class="hidden">
         <h3>下載進度</h3>
         <div class="progress-container">
           <div class="progress-bar">
             <div id="progressFill" class="progress-fill"></div>
           </div>
           <p id="progressText">0%</p>
           <p id="progressStatus">準備中...</p>
         </div>
       </div>
 
       <div id="error" class="hidden">
         <p id="errorMessage"></p>
       </div>
     </main>
 
     <footer>
       <p>注意：僅供個人學習與測試用途，請遵守 YouTube 服務條款</p>
       <button id="advanceBtn" style="margin-top:8px;padding:6px 16px;background:#e94560;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">進階模式</button>
     </footer>
   </div>
 
   <!-- Help Modal -->
   <div id="helpModal" class="modal-overlay hidden">
     <div class="modal-box">
       <button class="modal-close" id="helpClose">&times;</button>
       <h2>API 使用說明</h2>
       <h3>直接下載 API</h3>
       <p>直接透過瀏覽器或程式獲取影片/音訊串流，無需選擇格式，自動下載最高畫質。</p>
       <pre>影片 MP4：<br>http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/direct/video?url=<mark>YouTube連結</mark>
 
 音樂 M4A：<br>http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/direct/music?url=<mark>YouTube連結</mark></pre>
       <p>影片預設下載最高畫質 MP4 並自動合併音軌，音樂則為最高品質 M4A。</p>
       <h3>cURL 範例</h3>
       <pre># 下載 MP4
 curl -o video.mp4 "http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/direct/video?url=https://youtu.be/jNQXAC9IVRw"
 
 # 下載 M4A
 curl -o audio.m4a "http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/direct/music?url=https://youtu.be/jNQXAC9IVRw"</pre>
       <h3>Python 範例</h3>
       <pre>import requests
 url = "http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/direct/video"
 params = {"url": "https://youtu.be/jNQXAC9IVRw"}
 r = requests.get(url, params=params, stream=True)
 filename = r.headers.get("Content-Disposition", "").split("filename*=UTF-8''")[-1] or "video.mp4"
 with open(filename, "wb") as f:
     for chunk in r.iter_content(chunk_size=8192):
         f.write(chunk)
 print(f"下載完成: {filename}")</pre>
       <h3>JavaScript 範例</h3>
       <pre>// 直接觸發瀏覽器下載
 window.location.href = "http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/direct/video?url=https://youtu.be/jNQXAC9IVRw";
 
 // 非同步 fetch
 const res = await fetch("/public/downloadyt/api/direct/video?url=https://youtu.be/jNQXAC9IVRw");
 const blob = await res.blob();
 const a = document.createElement("a");
 a.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
 a.download = "video.mp4";
 a.click();</pre>
       <h3>進階「選格式」API：</h3>
       <pre># 先獲取可用格式列表
 curl -X POST http://伺服器IP:<%= port %>/public/downloadyt/api/formats \
   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
   -d '{"url":"https://youtu.be/jNQXAC9IVRw"}'</pre>
     </div>
   </div>
 
   <script src="<%= basePath %>/app.js"></script>
 </body>
 </html>
